headline: ONEOK (OKE) Asserts Shareholder Value Commitment with $1.03 Quarterly Dividend
summary: ONEOK, Inc. (NYSE:OKE) is one of the best depressed stocks to buy in 2025. On July 16, the company reiterated its commitment to shareholder value by maintaining a quarterly dividend of $1.03 a share. The quarterly dividend translates to an annualized dividend of $4.12 a share. The company will pay a $1.03 per share dividend […]
